  --   Returns numerical rank, estimate for the inverse condition number,
  --   and the singular value decomposition of A.

  -- ON ENTRY:
  --   A        matrix for which numerical rank is desired;
  --   tol      tolerance to decide the numerical rank.
  
  -- ON RETURN :
